com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.api

インタフェース Context

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    DefaultContext

    public interface Context
    A context to be used in subcomponents. The general idea of Context/Contextualizable was taken from Jakarta's Avalon framework.
    作成者:
    lkuehne
    関連項目:
    Contextualizable
